        <h1>
            Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM Business Solutions has created this statement in order to showcase our commitment
            to privacy, when you visit our website. This statement discloses the information
            practices for the CEM web site, including what type of information is gathered and
            tracked, how the information is used, and with whom the information is shared.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            <strong>Collection of Personal Information</strong></p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM respects your privacy. You are welcome to visit CEM website without revealing
            any information about your identity. To use certain features in this site, like
            submitting an enquiry, logging a case, downloading documents, etc., we require you
            to submit personal information, such as your name, job title, organization, organization's
            URL, email address or phone number.<br />
            We use a variety of security technologies and procedures to help protect your personal
            information from unauthorized access, use or disclosure. CEM does not divulge your
            information to any third party or parties outside CEM.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            <strong>Use of Cookies</strong></p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM uses cookies, which allocates unique identification to your system. Cookies
            also help CEM to make our site more responsive to your needs by delivering a personalized
            experience to you. The cookies are stored on your computer's hard disk and are used
            by CEM to track your navigation within our website.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM may store some information on your computer when you visit our site. We are
            able to read these cookies for information purposes when you revisit our website.
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            The type of information we gather as a result of a cookie being accepted by your
            computer is specific to your computer and includes the IP address, the date and
            time you visited our website, which sections of our website were looked at and whether
            the web pages requested were delivered successfully. This information does not include
            any of your personal information.
            <br />
            <br />
            We use the cookie information to improve our knowledge of the use of our website
            and to find out whether the website is functioning at an optimal level. This allows
            us to enhance our offerings to our customers and to provide a superior online experience.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            You can block this information being sent to us by changing the cookie settings
            on your computer. However, if you block this feature, you may not be able to utilize
            some features of our site.<strong> </strong>
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            <strong>Sharing of Information</strong></p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM does not divulge your information to any third party or parties outside CEM.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM may use your personal information from time to time for the following purposes:</p>
        <ul class="ul_reasons">
            <li>Market research and tracking of sales data</li>
            <li>Informing you about our products and services, which may include contacting you
                by email, fax, telephone or other means based on the information you have provided</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM does not advocate the practice of sending unsolicited mail. You are always welcome
            to indicate that you don't want us to use your information for further communication.<br />
            <br />
            CEM collects and uses anonymous information about visits to the site to help us
            provide better and more customer-friendly service by analyzing trends and patterns.
            For example, we keep track of the domains from which people visit us and we also
            measure visitor activity on the website. Any such information is only for the purpose
            of analysis at a macro level.<br />
            <br />
            This site contains links to other sites. CEM is not responsible for content, privacy
            practices or policies of other sites apart from those of its subsidiaries.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            <strong>Data Security</strong></p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM has deployed technology and policies to protect your privacy from unauthorized
            access and misuse. We store your personal information in our secure web server and
            protect it by implementing appropriate physical, electronic security safeguards.
            We use technologies such as firewall, enforce physical access controls to our files,
            and we authorize access to your information only for those personnel who require
            it to execute their job responsibilities.</p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            <strong>Change In Privacy Policy </strong>
        </p>
        <p style="text-align: justify;">
            CEM may make changes to this privacy policy. If we make any changes to the existing
            privacy policy, we will publish these changes on this page and will notify you of
            any significant changes. Please check our privacy policy on a regular basis.</p>
